import React, {useState} from 'react'
import { AppBar, IconButton } from '@mui/material'
import Box from '@mui/material/Box'
import Toolbar from '@mui/material/Toolbar'
import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography'
import Button from '@mui/material/Button'
import Avatar from '@mui/material/Avatar'
import { Link } from "react-router-dom"
import Menu from '@mui/material/Menu'
import HomeIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Home'
import Tooltip from '@mui/material/Tooltip';
import GroupsIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Groups';
import LocalShippingIcon from '@mui/icons-material/LocalShipping';
import NotesIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Notes';
import ShowChartIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ShowChart';
import AutoStoriesIcon from '@mui/icons-material/AutoStories';
import ScienceIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Science';

const Appbar = () => {

  return (
    <Box sx={{flexGrow: 1 }}>
        <AppBar position="static" color="transparent">
            <Toolbar>
                <Tooltip title="Home">
                <Link to="/home" underline="none">
                <IconButton
                    size="large"
                    edge="start"
                    color="inherit"
                    sx={{ mr:2 }}
                >
                    <HomeIcon/>
                </IconButton>
                </Link>
                </Tooltip>
                <Typography variant="h6"> 
                    Virginia Sage
                </Typography>
                <Tooltip title="The Team">
                    <Button color="inherit" href="team" endIcon={<GroupsIcon/>} >The Team </Button>
                </Tooltip>
                <Tooltip title="Deliverables">
                        <Button color="inherit" href="deliverables" endIcon={<LocalShippingIcon/>} >Deliverables </Button>
                </Tooltip>
                <Tooltip title="User Stories">
                        <Button color="inherit" href="userstories" endIcon={<AutoStoriesIcon/>} >User Stories</Button>
                </Tooltip>
                <Tooltip title="Presentations">
                    <Link to="/presentations" underline="none">
                        <Button color="inherit" href="presentations" endIcon={<ShowChartIcon/>} >Presentations</Button>
                    </Link>
                </Tooltip>
                <Tooltip title="Labs">
                    <Link to="labs">
                        <Button color="inherit" endIcon={<ScienceIcon/>} >Labs</Button>
                    </Link>
                </Tooltip>
                <Tooltip title="References">
                    <Link to="/references">
                        <Button color="inherit" endIcon={<NotesIcon/>} >References </Button>
                    </Link>
                </Tooltip>
            </Toolbar>
        </AppBar>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Appbar
